@startuml
title Complete state diagram of ATM withdrawal process

[*] --> Selection
state Selection
state CustomValue
state Verification
state Rejection
state Confirmation
state Completed
state Cancelled

Selection --> CustomValue : select custom value
Selection --> Verification : select from list

CustomValue --> Verification : validate / send amount to verify

Verification --> Rejection : reject / send user.rejection
Verification --> Confirmation : confirm / send user.confirmation
Verification --> Cancelled : cancel

Confirmation --> Completed : dispense cash and receipt
Confirmation --> Cancelled : cancel transaction

Rejection --> Selection : re-enter amount
Cancelled --> [*] : return to initial state
Completed --> [*] : return to initial state
@enduml
